<p class="p1">Triangular crayons for tub-time creativity. <strong>Honeysticks Bath Crayon Triangles 10pk</strong> are the perfect first step into bath-time art. With their clever triangle shape, they’re easy to grip, won’t roll away, and are made with pure beeswax and soy wax for safe, sensory play.</p>
<ul class="ul1">
<li class="li1">
<span class="s1"></span><b>Shaped for small hands:</b> The triangle design encourages grip development and early mark-making – perfect for little artists just getting started. Plus, it won’t roll off the tub mid-play. When they’re ready for the next stage, try our Honeysticks Bath Crayon Super Jumbos.</li>
<li class="li1">
<span class="s1"></span><b>Creative confidence, built in the bath:</b> Support sensory learning, coordination and imagination, all while making a splash.</li>
<li class="li1">
<span class="s1"></span><b>Ten vibrant colours to explore:</b> For drawing, doodling, and colour-filled fun that washes off when the fun is done.</li>
<li class="li1">
<span class="s1"></span><b>No nasties, just pure creativity:</b> Crafted with natural beeswax and soy wax, plus food-grade colourants. Safe for play, safe for planet.</li>
<li class="li1">
<span class="s1"></span><b>Wipes clean with warm water:</b> No scrubbing needed – a gentle wipe and the tub is ready for next time.</li>
<li class="li1">
<span class="s1"></span><b>Lovingly handmade in New Zealand:</b> Created by parents who believe in a better way to play – safe, sustainable, and designed to inspire from the very first splash.</li>
</ul>
<p class="p1"><em><b>Now in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation!</b></em></p>
